{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content-editor-core lake-engine lake-typography-classic\" data-lake-element=\"root\" data-selection-undefined=\"%7B%22path%22%3A%5B%5B0%2C0%2C15%5D%2C%5B0%2C0%2C15%5D%5D%2C%22active%22%3Atrue%7D\"><h1 data-lake-id=\"56bd30996d868b1ba0d0b1a38fd510f3\" id=\"mGEBo\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;\">直接在 gingko 中查看：</h1><p data-lake-id=\"8add94f5a8b3aaf241000589a17816cd\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span><br></span></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"bookmarklink\" id=\"oakqf\"><a href=\"https://gingkoapp.com/am2or8\" style=\"\n    word-wrap: break-word;\n    color: #096DD9;\n    touch-action: manipulation;\n    background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0);\n    text-decoration: none;\n    outline: none;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: color .3s;\n  \">原链接</a></div><p data-lake-id=\"1c628ce38d31a01104646fa8ab59bf16\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"810fc3e0d2f2167e622e1e0ceb1ad988\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"image\" class=\"lake-card-margin-top lake-card-margin-bottom\"><img data-role=\"image\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/995602/1597328780845-fe75c1be-6047-4889-a0f1-34974680eac1.png\" data-raw-src=\"\" class=\"image lake-drag-image\" alt=\"image.png\" title=\"image.png\" data-height=\"540px\" style=\"visibility: visible; width: 960px;\"></span></p><h1 id=\"39cacbb9\" data-lake-id=\"f1f46ebb17f7dbc8f6b04bcf1f73caa2\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;\">独特的内容展示方式</h1><p data-lake-id=\"d6316460baa0baf776af1bb48d922c75\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 id=\"a54c3e48\" data-lake-id=\"4123c3c1aec78e6818f8ca49a485391b\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">平铺展示所有内容的树状结构</h2><p data-lake-id=\"4abd841d21b513e5e442abe24a4f9a28\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"1284666fadf73280700f92de0668859d\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">gingko 可以创建多个页面, 每个页面称为一棵 gingko 树, 每一棵 gingko 树由很多张 markdown 卡片组成, 其内容组织形式本质上是树状结构, 比如 A1 和 A2 这两张卡片隶属于 A, B1 和 B3 又隶属于 B.</p><p data-lake-id=\"c3f2aba3215e00fedc77712679103407\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"c3231a31ac8112e9d11d0f1b1ded4ba1\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">树状结构并不稀奇, gingko 最大的特点在于, 它把所有卡片的所有<strong>内容</strong>全部平铺展示在同一个界面上, 因此用户可以纵览全局, 发掘出 A1 和 B3 这种不同分支上卡片的逻辑联系, 并灵活地重组内容结构.</p><p data-lake-id=\"6e9c23e605e9098c566aa912c26942ba\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"31d8a0f4c0f49737577edecd98666f90\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">在不需要浏览所有卡片时, 也可以针对单张卡片进入全屏模式编辑, 排除干扰.</p><p data-lake-id=\"cd6cb35d5592156cf362f5868de60d32\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 id=\"4c63455b\" data-lake-id=\"24b53b0d7aefef5b3c4b8cf9f72f1b66\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">稀疏树</h2><p data-lake-id=\"cbeccf30c01c64b97d4d31a75541e76b\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"3aa5c786596a118d2e50c17aec57478b\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">gingko 的搜索只能搜索当前页面, 跟直接使用浏览器的页内搜索不同, gingko 的搜索会过滤掉不包含搜索关键词的卡片, 让整个页面上只剩下包含关键词的卡片, 也就是生成了一颗稀疏树.</p><p data-lake-id=\"b27398f1fa56583ad731748aaad12f07\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"131bfa63042b7354fbca32bfff6c7e47\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">使用树状结构组织内容的软件很多, 但是能生成稀疏树的不多, 这实际上是一个很有用的功能, 可以让用户聚焦到跟某一个小主题相关的所有卡片, 而不必在所有内容里上上下下翻来找去.</p><p data-lake-id=\"3f8cafd24e0e45de87f9243b1d570db6\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 id=\"aca57226\" data-lake-id=\"083072c8ba4ea4d8fdf4709888fac0d1\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">trash 与树状结构</h2><p data-lake-id=\"64108336971ff95e97a7c55236a7e6a7\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"e6c90687b8472dd84a23fc9ddc854a73\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">在其它软件里, trash 的作用仅仅是让用户可以恢复删除的内容, 而 gingko 用了一种别出心裁的方式来利用 trash. 当用户选择 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">show trash</code>, 所有被删除的卡片会出现在它们原本所在的位置, 这种展示方式可以辅助用户做出判断: 是一键恢复这张卡片还是彻底删除它.</p><p data-lake-id=\"66278ce26b4a5924f578b2afc30cdcab\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h1 id=\"d3e74352\" data-lake-id=\"f625129270461d7d63b2807bd97223da\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;\">并不独特但是又很重要的通用功能</h1><p data-lake-id=\"375c9676c4e8844660c3a7bcb93a2618\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 id=\"14cc0286\" data-lake-id=\"1d18fb671d17371570bcbe302166ab56\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">全键盘操作</h2><p data-lake-id=\"870e5a20a9cffb11d6113eac587e0a98\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><ul data-lake-id=\"1ad7f035dcf8a4057f1480561b3cff84\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li data-lake-id=\"e57890b601b7d250e31b58d424efb351\">卡片的创建/移动/删除/合并/切分可以靠快捷键完成.</li><li data-lake-id=\"f133f2de5bd22d2b3e9e59c20a0580e5\">编辑模式和全屏模式的切换和退出可以靠快捷键完成.</li><li data-lake-id=\"562af4360940bb35929d6c00afcbfd26\">焦点的切换可以靠方向键完成.</li><li data-lake-id=\"c03d7ee2813ed881892cfafd656f6805\">所有用到方向键的地方都可以用 Vim 风格的 HJKL 四个键代替.</li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"b16cd96752bcc4a6b871cd7f925b0bef\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 id=\"62890d1b\" data-lake-id=\"4c64d4bb3ffd0ef741725fe9586116e1\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">比较丰富的导出功能</h2><p data-lake-id=\"96755c64e6f818cf280e7dd4adfe6589\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"66e990a6a36a5aff46a820f4c9be402d\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">gingko 有比较丰富的导出格式和比较细致的导出选项, 导出之前无需手动把卡片排成线性, gingko 会自动按照树状结构来决定卡片在最终导出文档里的顺序.</p><p data-lake-id=\"805ad40c77976a57fe5ceec1131594dc\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 id=\"449dabd0\" data-lake-id=\"98c7e66a8303b06a495b479dd063d609\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">协作与分享</h2><p data-lake-id=\"213bb978abe472d7be0111fe62088ab7\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"6ab60200a3ebeaf5715c3438333632e4\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">gingko 的分享方式很灵活, 一棵 gingko 树可以用链接形式来分享, 其它人无需注册也能查看, 注册用户之间也可以合作编辑.</p><p data-lake-id=\"ce63f272b1dafb65d1167ddfcb072a30\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"6b42cad02a0232fcb4e87012449bbb72\" id=\"EZfzb\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;\">数学公式</h1><p data-lake-id=\"d16deab31e50bba9e38e9b2cdc6b5a6b\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">gingko 支持 mathjax 数学公式，这在写作 app 中是很少见的。据说作者当年开发 gingko 就是为了应付 phd 论文，不过根据我这么久的使用感受，真要用它应付 phd 论文还是捉襟见肘。</p><h1 id=\"4bda7612\" data-lake-id=\"8c2465204dd969cf004824a2938540ed\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;\">功能之外的优点</h1><p data-lake-id=\"7c97a31d225253e7ed8a3cd893a763ec\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><ul data-lake-id=\"517b7e9e468fbfebbfbec3eabda2ae32\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li data-lake-id=\"6f0565cbf2284aeab5767fc6d23322a7\">web app, 无需安装.</li><li data-lake-id=\"d6e32d158188cccc8175197c4fc41d03\">中国用户无需科学上网就能使用.</li><li data-lake-id=\"4f77cfd87535aa548713e76dfc51fe1b\">大多数国外软件的价格在数字上和国内同类软件一样, 但是一美元和一人民币是不一样的, 所以整体来说国外软件要贵得多, 而 gingko 的最低价格($2 per month)能让更多的人接受; 免费版也只有卡片数量上的限制, 没有功能上的限制.</li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"522a8cc04921ef31f786593bc9b6751c\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h1 id=\"2e769a75\" data-lake-id=\"67da5d4c326dba655c162d93bc991514\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;\">缺点</h1><p data-lake-id=\"aa5104cd2d35a8871826088d82d82b68\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 id=\"c1c385fb\" data-lake-id=\"88873c3b832e366beffdd229f65669b8\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">卡片字数太多影响平铺效果</h2><p data-lake-id=\"8a05f9e3f6fd59d299a876b42f8c36d3\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"6a9cfe785ba6c33bc9762112cbb4e902\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">虽然说平铺所有卡片的内容确实能达到一种鸟瞰的效果, 但假如卡片里的字数较多, 整个屏幕就显示不了多少卡片, 特别是在十几寸屏幕的笔记本上.</p><p data-lake-id=\"cb6a7424d9740d64893cd6f5bed93461\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 id=\"4ad5327f\" data-lake-id=\"3ee30b662a7637dea67ae3a1c6c99a44\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">没有字数统计</h2><p data-lake-id=\"e3dc94e9cd4548530ef8502b830474f1\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"69cf089d7f2475f96bf32fc881659170\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">网页版 gingko 是没有字数统计功能的, 新出的半成品桌面版虽然加入了字数统计, 但是不支持统计以中文为代表的无空格语言.</p><p data-lake-id=\"96d71f7dd7a7dc59765689b5651ffbb5\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 id=\"dca49e84\" data-lake-id=\"ad39fa25ba9d6682188bf8c0b715bae5\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">没有批量替换功能</h2><p data-lake-id=\"a5167ac68c38f5a41235f0514c126449\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"6b51b9673b15645ea2c920537e027f96\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">可以说是 web app 的通病了.</p><p data-lake-id=\"b4799c185d26b66da415fa011d428a01\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 id=\"58503306\" data-lake-id=\"3d63b0606be8c134a8dcfc09a14e7006\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">开发进度缓慢</h2><p data-lake-id=\"ca6fd3882037b667c051d078191e3704\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"145c30a5caf3e5155c96133d1067b938\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">gingko 的开发者只有一个人, 再加上没有同类竞品, 所以开发进度缓慢.</p><p data-lake-id=\"afde6f5138995bca5bc15cd346fa9206\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 id=\"4bc0fa83\" data-lake-id=\"34c7858210a066d32abff4c656dc6649\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">没有自带图床</h2><p data-lake-id=\"ec793ee5812249e430690bde4530bb74\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"c28e6d37cbc617f21de1d4a3544fec40\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">同样是使用 markdown 的 web app, Dynalist 是可以直接把图片复制进去并自动上传的的, 但是 gingko 不支持这么做,只能靠 url 的方式插入链接.</p></div>",
  "slug": 8311646,
  "title": "gingko - 平铺式卡片写作"
}